(2, 'Lim o lavagna in ardesia? Tu che dici? ', 'Alessandro Metz - Redazione 22-23', 'Al giorno d’oggi la Lim sta spodestando la lavagna in ardesia diventando la più utilizzata per le sue varie qualità, ma cosa ne pensano gli studenti? ', '2024-05-30', '[\"Negli%20ultimi%20anni%20si%20%C3%A8%20dibattuto%20se%20fosse%20meglio%20la%20lavagna%20in%20ardesia%20o%20la%20lim.%20Abbiamo%20chiesto%20ad%20alcuni%20alunni%20cosa%20ne%20pensassero%20e%20la%20maggior%20parte%20ritiene%20che%20la%20lavagna%20digitale%20sia%20nettamente%20migliore%20rispetto%20a%20quella%20in%20ardesia%3B%20ma%20cosa%20dicono%20i%20fatti%3F%20\",\"La%20Lim%20viene%20utilizzata%20di%20pi%C3%B9%20di%20quella%20in%20ardesia%2C%20%C3%A8%20molto%20pratica%20perch%C3%A9%20permette%20di%20inviare%20i%20file%20della%20lezione%20agli%20studenti%20che%20possono%20cos%C3%AC%20integrare%20i%20loro%20appunti.%20La%20lavagna%20digitale%20%C3%A8%20semplice%20da%20utilizzare%20ma%20richiede%20allenamento%20per%20essere%20usata%20con%20facilit%C3%A0%20e%2C%20a%20chi%20non%20%C3%A8%20mai%20capitato%20che%20abbia%20toccato%20dove%20non%20doveva%20e%20non%20sapeva%20cosa%20fare%3F%20Tutto%20evitabile%20con%20un%20po%E2%80%99%20di%20esperienza%20e%20abilit%C3%A0%20pratiche.%20\",\"La%20lavagna%20in%20ardesia%20%C3%A8%20pi%C3%B9%20semplice%20da%20utilizzare%20anche%20se%20presenta%20varie%20scomodit%C3%A0%3A%20per%20pulirla%20si%20rischia%20di%20sporcarsi%20con%20il%20gesso%2C%20se%20la%20lavagna%20%C3%A8%20piena%20di%20scritte%20e%20bisogna%20aggiungere%20dell%E2%80%99altro%2C%20cancellando%2C%20si%20perdono%20parti%20di%20spiegazione%20che%20non%20possono%20essere%20recuperate.%20Tuttavia%20scrivere%20sulla%20lavagna%20con%20il%20gesso%20d%C3%A0%20una%20sensazione%20diversa%2C%20mescola%20i%20ricordi%20e%20le%20emozioni%20passate%20di%20quando%20eravamo%20piccoli.\",\"In%20conclusione%20la%20Lim%20%C3%A8%20sicuramente%20la%20lavagna%20con%20pi%C3%B9%20qualit%C3%A0%20e%20meno%20difetti%20tra%20le%20due%2C%20ma%20io%20prediligo%20la%20vecchia%20lavagna%20in%20ardesia%20per%20le%20sensazioni%20che%20mi%20fa%20provare%20ogni%20volta%20che%20la%20utilizzo%20portando%20la%20mia%20mente%20nel%20mondo%20dei%20ricordi.%20\"]', 'https://i.ibb.co/0M2wZLg/IMG2.png', 'https://i.ibb.co/0M2wZLg/IMG2.png', '{\"intervista\":\"\",\"in lingua\":\"\",\"politica studentesca\":\"\",\"fatti dal mondo\":\"\",\"salute e benessere\":\"\",\"editoriale\":\"\"}'),
(3, 'DDI: perché no?', 'Samuele Colautti – Redazione 22-23', 'Appunto, perché? La DDI (Didattica Digitale Integrata) è stata un’ottima soluzione nei tempi più critici della pandemia da COVID-19: ha infatti permesso a studenti e alunni di proseguire le lezioni anche quando non sembrava più possibile, permettendo al sistema scolastico italiano di subire meno danni possibile. ', '', '[\"Recentemente%2C%20cure%20e%20accortezze%20da%20parte%20dei%20cittadini%20hanno%20ridotto%20l%E2%80%99impatto%20del%20COVID%20sulle%20nostre%20vite%20permettendoci%20di%20tornare%20a%20qualcosa%20di%20simile%20alla%20vita%20precedente%20la%20pandemia%2C%20e%20la%20DDI%20%C3%A8%20stata%20messa%20da%20parte%2C%20in%20quanto%20ritenuta%20la%20causa%20del%20forte%20calo%20del%20rendimento%20scolastico%20di%20molti%20studenti.%20C%E2%80%99%C3%A8%20chi%20parla%20di%20fallimento%20della%20DAD%20ed%20%C3%A8%20convinto%20che%20questo%20metodo%20d%E2%80%99insegnamento%20abbia%20escluso%20molti%20alunni%20con%20difficolt%C3%A0%20di%20vario%20genere.%20\",\"Io%20credo%20semplicemente%20che%20la%20pandemia%20ci%20abbia%20colti%20impreparati%20%28giustamente%2C%20insomma%2C%20nessuno%20poteva%20prevederla%29%20e%20ci%20abbia%20costretto%20a%20correre%20ai%20ripari%2C%20a%20trovare%20soluzioni%20efficienti%20in%20poco%20tempo.%20Purtroppo%2C%20abbiamo%20tutti%20imparato%20a%20nostre%20spese%20che%20le%20soluzioni%20efficaci%20necessitano%20di%20molto%20tempo%20per%20essere%20elaborate.%20\",\"Secondo%20me%2C%20per%C3%B2%2C%20la%20DDI%20%C3%A8%20un%20valido%20strumento%20che%20ha%20ancora%20molto%20da%20offrire%3A%20io%20stesso%2C%20come%20tutti%20i%20miei%20coetanei%2C%20d%E2%80%99altronde%2C%20ho%20provato%20l%E2%80%99esperienza%20della%20DAD%20in%20prima%20persona%20e%20ho%20trovato%20molti%20punti%20deboli%20nel%20sistema%20che%20impedivano%20il%20corretto%20proseguire%20delle%20lezioni%20a%20distanza%3A%20tutti%20errori%20dovuti%20al%20poco%20tempo%20a%20disposizione%20per%20adattarsi%20ad%20una%20situazione%20decisamente%20inusuale%20per%20tutti%20e%20che%20adesso%2C%20con%20pi%C3%B9%20calma%2C%20possono%20essere%20risolti.%20\",\"Prima%20non%20potevamo%20permetterci%20di%20fermarci%20a%20riflettere%20su%20cosa%20funzionava%20e%20cosa%20no%2C%20ma%20ora%20che%20non%20abbiamo%20scadenze%20da%20rispettare%2C%20possiamo%20tutti%20imparare%20di%20nuovo%2C%20prendendoci%20il%20tempo%20che%20ci%20serve%2C%20in%20modo%20non%20solo%20da%20poter%20usare%20meglio%20la%20DDI%20in%20un%20nuovo%20%28malaugurato%29%20periodo%20di%20emergenza%2C%20ma%20anche%20di%20essere%20capaci%20di%20integrarla%20nella%20nostra%20quotidianit%C3%A0%20scolastica%2C%20ad%20esempio%20per%20risolvere%20una%20serie%20di%20frequenti%20problematiche%20che%20spesso%20interferiscono%20con%20l%E2%80%99apprendimento%2C%20in%20presenza%20o%20a%20distanza%20che%20sia.%20\",\"Se%20riuscissimo%20ad%20integrare%20questo%20strumento%20nella%20vita%20di%20tutti%20i%20giorni%2C%20si%20potrebbe%20permettere%20ad%20uno%20studente%20assente%20di%20continuare%20a%20seguire%20le%20lezioni%20o%20ad%20un%20professore%20di%20svolgere%20uno%20sportello%20pomeridiano%20senza%20il%20problema%20di%20alunni%20che%20non%20hanno%20possibilit%C3%A0%20di%20tornare%20a%20scuola%20in%20quell%E2%80%99orario.%20\",\"Insomma%2C%20con%20qualche%20miglioria%2C%20secondo%20me%2C%20la%20DDI%20pu%C3%B2%20ancora%20rivelarsi%20molto%20utile.%20Col%20tempo%2C%20naturalmente.%20\"]', 'https://i.ibb.co/bNCHp0P/IMG3.png', 'https://i.ibb.co/bNCHp0P/IMG3.png', '{\"intervista\":\"\",\"in lingua\":\"\",\"politica studentesca\":\"\",\"fatti dal mondo\":\"\",\"salute e benessere\":\"\",\"editoriale\":\"\"}'),
(4, 'La Preside si racconta', 'Nicol Versolato, Emmamaria Zannier – Redazione 22-23', 'Vi siete mai chiesti cosa si nasconda dietro al ruolo di Dirigente scolastica? Beh noi della classe 1^F si! Per questo abbiamo chiesto alla dottoressa Carla Bianchi se fosse disponibile a rispondere alle nostre domande. ', '2024-05-30', '[\"%3Cb%3EBuongiorno%20Dirigente%2C%20benvenuta.%20Cominciamo%20dalla%20prima%20curiosit%C3%A0%3A%20perch%C3%A9%20ha%20voluto%20diventare%20dirigente%20scolastica%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Da%20studentessa%20intrapresi%20gli%20studi%20magistrali.%20All%E2%80%99universit%C3%A0%20studiai%20vigilanza%20scolastica%2C%20per%20poi%20seguire%20il%20percorso%20come%20insegnante%20della%20primaria.%20Dopo%20vent%E2%80%99anni%20attraverso%20un%20concorso%2C%20riuscii%20a%20diventare%20dirigente%20scolastica.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EQuali%20sono%20i%20compiti%20della%20dirigente%20scolastica%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Da%20dirigente%20ho%20il%20compito%20di%20rappresentare%20legalmente%20l%E2%80%99Istituto%2C%20gestire%20e%20organizzare%20il%20lavoro%20di%20docenti%20e%20collaboratori.%20Inoltre%20sono%20responsabile%20dell%E2%80%99attivit%C3%A0%20economico-amministrativa%2C%20della%20sicurezza%2C%20della%20salute%20dei%20lavoratori%20e%20degli%20studenti%2C%20delle%20relazioni%20con%20l%E2%80%99esterno.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EQuali%20sono%20le%20differenze%20tra%20il%20ruolo%20di%20Preside%20e%20quello%20di%20Reggente%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Il%20Preside%20%C3%A8%20il%20titolare%20di%20un%E2%80%99istituzione%20scolastica.%20Il%20Reggente%20%C3%A8%20un%20preside%20a%20cui%20viene%20affidata%20la%20gestione%20di%20un%20secondo%20Istituto.%20Entrambi%20hanno%20le%20stesse%20responsabilit%C3%A0.%20E%E2%80%99%20come%20essere%20uno%20studente%20iscritto%20nello%20stesso%20momento%20in%20due%20classi%20prime%20di%20due%20scuole%20diverse.%20Il%20dirigente%20scolastico%20prende%203.200%2C00%20%E2%82%AC%20al%20mese%20e%20con%20la%20reggenza%20si%20aggiungono%20400%20%E2%82%AC%20al%20mese.%20\",\"%3Cb%3ECome%20si%20svolge%20la%20sua%20giornata%20a%20scuola%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Arrivo%20a%20scuola%20verso%20le%2008%3A30%3B%20lavoro%20in%20ufficio%3B%20ricevo%20studenti%2C%20docenti%2C%20genitori%3B%20svolgo%20attivit%C3%A0%20con%20i%20vicari%2C%20con%20la%20segreteria%20e%20il%20segretario%20amministrativo.%20Nel%20pomeriggio%20ci%20sono%20spesso%20delle%20attivit%C3%A0%20come%20i%20consigli%20di%20classe%20%28dalle%2014%20alle%2019%29.%20Non%20c%E2%80%99%C3%A8%20una%20pausa%20pranzo%20o%2C%20meglio%2C%20spesso%20si%20salta.%20Non%20ho%20un%20orario%20di%20lavoro%20fisso%2C%20ho%20il%20cartellino%20come%20il%20personale%20ATA%20per%20mia%20scelta.%20La%20mia%20attivit%C3%A0%20dovrebbe%20occupare%20le%2036%20ore%20settimanali%20ma%20in%20realt%C3%A0%20ne%20dedico%2040%2F42.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EPreferisce%20il%20ruolo%20di%20Insegnante%20o%20quello%20di%20Dirigente%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Fare%20l%E2%80%99insegnante%20%C3%A8%20un%20lavoro%20molto%20in%20teressante%20e%20coinvolgente.%20Gli%20studenti%20avvertono%20quando%20un%20insegnante%20lo%20fa%20per%20passione%20o%20per%20necessit%C3%A0.%20Da%20dirigente%20scolastica%20ti%20accorgi%20che%20non%20tutto%20%C3%A8%20fattibile%20come%20ti%20eri%20immaginato.%20Il%20rapporto%20con%20gli%20studenti%20manca.%20Si%20guadagna%2C%20per%C3%B2%2C%20nella%20relazione%20con%20le%20persone%20%28studenti%20e%20personale%20della%20scuola%29.\",\"%3Cb%3EQuali%20sono%20state%20le%20decisioni%20pi%C3%B9%20difficili%20da%20prendere%20in%20questi%20anni%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"A%20mio%20parere%20le%20decisioni%20pi%C3%B9%20difficili%20da%20prendere%20in%20questi%20anni%20sono%20state%2C%20durante%20il%20periodo%20di%20COVID%2C%20la%20sospensione%20di%20alcuni%20docenti%20per%20la%20questione%20vaccinale%3B%20intervenire%20in%20una%20situazione%20che%20ha%20comportato%20l%E2%80%99allontanamento%20di%20uno%20studente%20dalla%20sua%20famiglia%20e%20la%20gestione%20di%20uno%20studente%20che%20aveva%20commesso%20dei%20reati%3A%20avevamo%20molto%20sperato%20nel%20suo%20cambiamento.%20\",\"%3Cb%3ECosa%20l%E2%80%99ha%20resa%20pi%C3%B9%20orgogliosa%20da%20dirigente%20scolastica%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Uno%20degli%20orgogli%20pi%C3%B9%20belli%20%C3%A8%20stato%20quando%20ci%20hanno%20riconosciuti%20come%20miglior%20liceo%20della%20Regione.%20Inoltre%20%C3%A8%20una%20grande%20soddisfazione%20quando%20i%20genitori%20riconoscono%20che%20questa%20%C3%A8%20una%20scuola%20in%20cui%20gli%20studenti%20sono%20trattati%20come%20persone.%20\",\"%3Cb%3ELe%20%C3%A8%20mai%20capitato%20di%20sospendere%20degli%20alunni%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Mi%20%C3%A8%20successo%20poche%20volte%20di%20sospendere%20gli%20studenti.%20Quelle%20poche%20volte%20che%20%C3%A8%20successo%20%C3%A8%20stato%20a%20causa%20di%20superalcolici%20messi%20in%20valigia%20durante%20il%20viaggio%20di%20istruzione%2C%20per%20l%E2%80%99utilizzo%20del%20laboratorio%20di%20informatica%20per%20divulgare%20delle%20foto%20intime%20di%20una%20compagna%20e%20per%20la%20pubblicazione%20in%20rete%20di%20filmati%20girati%20di%20nascosto%20a%20scuola.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EQuali%20sono%20i%20lati%20positivi%20e%20negativi%20dell%E2%80%99avere%20tre%20sedi%3F%20%28si%20fa%20riferimento%20all%E2%80%99a.s.%202022-2023%2C%20ndr%29%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Un%20lato%20positivo%20%C3%A8%20che%20i%20licei%20si%20stanno%20ampliando%2C%20mentre%20quello%20negativo%20%C3%A8%20che%20le%20sedi%20si%20trovano%20distanti.%20Inoltre%20la%20scuola%20sta%20pensando%20di%20organizzarsi%20diversamente%20gi%C3%A0%20dal%20prossimo%20anno.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EQuali%20sono%20le%20spese%20della%20scuola%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Bisogna%20fare%20una%20distinzione%20tra%20spese%20di%20gestione%20%28pagate%20dall%E2%80%99ex%20provincia%3A%20riscaldamento%2C%20manutenzione%2C%20energia%20elettrica%29%20e%20spese%20di%20gestione%20amministrativa%20e%20didattica.%20i%20soldi%20vincolati%20a%20determinati%20obiettivi%20sono%20circa%20600.000%20%E2%82%AC.%20Per%20ogni%20alunno%20si%20spende%20mediamente%20590%2C00%20%E2%82%AC%20e%20la%20spesa%20amministrativa%20ammonta%20a%2078%2C00%20%E2%82%AC.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EQual%20era%20il%20suo%20sogno%20da%20bambina%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Da%20bambina%20sognavo%20di%20studiare%20medicina%20per%20poi%20diventare%20medico.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EQual%20%C3%A8%20il%20suo%20primo%20ricordo%20della%20scuola%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Il%20mio%20primo%20ricordo%20della%20scuola%20%C3%A8%20che%20iniziava%20il%20primo%20di%20ottobre%3B%20quelli%20del%20primo%20anno%20venivano%20chiamati%20remigini%20%28da%20S.Remigio%20che%20%C3%A8%20il%20santo%20che%20si%20celebra%20il%20primo%20ottobre%29.%20Il%20primo%20ricordo%20del%20mio%20primo%20giorno%20di%20scuola%20elementare%20%C3%A8%20un%20cappellino%20di%20cartoncino%20rosso%20e%20la%20mia%20fierezza%20di%20portarlo%20in%20testa.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EChe%20scuola%20ha%20frequentato%20e%20qual%20era%20la%20sua%20materia%20preferita%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Ho%20frequentato%20il%20Marco%20Belli.%20Fino%20alla%20terza%20avevo%20due%20materie%20preferite%3A%20matematica%20e%20latino.%20Dalla%20terza%20in%20poi%20ho%20preferito%20il%20latino.%20\",\"%3Cb%3ENoi%20quest%E2%80%99anno%20abbiamo%20affrontato%20il%20passaggio%20dalle%20scuole%20medie%20alle%20superiori.%20Si%20ricorda%20come%20lo%20ha%20vissuto%20lei%20da%20ragazza%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"All%E2%80%99epoca%20si%20sceglieva%20l%E2%80%99istituto%20superiore%20senza%20poter%20vedere%20prima%20la%20scuola.%20Non%20ho%20scelto%20il%20liceo%20nonostante%20il%20consiglio%20orientativo%20dei%20professori%20delle%20scuole%20medie.%20I%20miei%20genitori%20erano%20insegnanti%20e%20quindi%20ho%20seguito%20la%20loro%20strada.%20\",\"%3Cb%3ECome%20si%20svolgeva%20l%E2%80%99esame%20di%20maturit%C3%A0%20quando%20lo%20ha%20sostenuto%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"C%E2%80%99erano%20due%20materie%20scritte%2C%20italiano%20e%20matematica.%20All%E2%80%99orale%20si%20portavano%20due%20materie%20ma%20bisognava%20studiarle%20tutte.%20C%E2%80%99era%20una%20commissione%20esterna%20e%20un%20solo%20e%20unico%20commissario%20interno.%20L%E2%80%99esperienza%20%C3%A8%20stata%20abbastanza%20positiva%20anche%20se%20il%20voto%20finale%20non%20ha%20corrisposto%20alle%20mie%20aspettative%20%2858%20anzich%C3%A8%2060%2F60%29.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EQuali%20sono%20le%20sue%20passioni%20oltre%20la%20scuola%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Una%20mia%20passione%20%C3%A8%20la%20musica%3A%20mi%20piace%20molto%20cantare.%20Poi%20mi%20piace%20mantenermi%20in%20forma%20infatti%20vado%20a%20correre%2C%20camminare%20e%20infine%20adoro%20viaggiare.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EE%E2%80%99%20mai%20stata%20bocciata%2C%20rimandata%20o%20ha%20mai%20ricevuto%20una%20nota%20disciplinare%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"No%2C%20non%20mi%20%C3%A8%20mai%20capitato.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EConsiderando%20l%E2%80%99impegno%20del%20suo%20lavoro%20come%20riesce%20a%20staccare%20la%20mente%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Basta%20pensare%20che%20al%20lavoro%20ci%20sono%20delle%20cose%20da%20fare%2C%20a%20casa%20altre%20e%20bisogna%20occuparsi%20al%20meglio%20di%20quello%20che%20si%20sta%20facendo%20in%20quell%E2%80%99esatto%20momento.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EQuali%20differenze%20generazionali%20ha%20notato%20negli%20alunni%20in%20questi%20ultimi%20dieci%20anni%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Ho%20notato%20una%20certa%20immaturit%C3%A0%20nei%20ragazzi%20di%20prima%20rispetto%20a%20dieci%20anni%20fa%2C%20mentre%20nei%20periodi%20pi%C3%B9%20recenti%20la%20dipendenza%20da%20telefonino%20mi%20preoccupa%20molto%3A%20rende%20la%20persona%20un%20mondo%20a%20s%C3%A8.%20Bisognerebbe%20promuovere%20la%20consapevolezza%20nell%E2%80%99utilizzo.%20\",\"%3Cb%3ECosa%20pensa%20degli%20insegnanti%20giovani%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Molti%20insegnanti%20giovani%20giovani%20hanno%20un%20approccio%20entusiasta%20alla%20scuola%2C%20estremamente%20positivo%2C%20vengono%20con%20piacere%20e%20con%20passione.%20Talvolta%20capita%20anche%20un%20docente%20giovane%20ma%20con%20mentalit%C3%A0%20vecchia%20e%20ingessata%20e%20questo%20mi%20spaventa%20ma%20ho%20fiducia%20nel%20mio%20team%21\"]', 'https://i.ibb.co/crVBst9/IMG4.png', 'https://i.ibb.co/crVBst9/IMG4.png', '{\"intervista\":\"1\",\"in lingua\":\"\",\"politica studentesca\":\"\",\"fatti dal mondo\":\"\",\"salute e benessere\":\"\",\"editoriale\":\"\"}'),
(5, 'Le attività degli studenti all’estero ', 'Gabriele Focarelli, Rares Ionut Nistor', 'Da molti anni la nostra scuola intrattiene buoni rapporti con altre scuole nel mondo e crea con queste interessanti progetti didattici e interculturali. ', '2024-05-30', '[\"Our%20school%20has%20always%20had%20good%20relationships%20with%20people%20from%20different%20countries%20for%20many%20years%20and%20consequently%20it%20has%20created%20interesting%20projects%20with%20other%20schools%20around%20the%20world.%20For%20example%2C%20this%20year%20some%20students%20from%20Chile%20came%20to%20our%20school%20to%20experience%20a%20cultural%20exchange.%20They%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20attend%20our%20school%20to%20learn%20about%20our%20language%20and%20culture.%20Then%2C%20during%20the%20summer%208%20Italian%20students%20from%20our%20school%20will%20leave%20for%20Chile%20to%20experience%20the%20language%20and%20the%20culture%20of%20this%20hosting%20country.%20\",\"Other%20activities%20that%20are%20organized%20during%20the%20year%20are%20called%20%E2%80%9CStages%E2%80%9D%3A%20these%20are%20a%20one%20week%20stay%20abroad%20especially%20for%20students%20from%20Liceo%20Linguistico.%20During%20this%20experience%20students%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20go%20abroad%20to%20European%20countries%20like%2C%20for%20example%20Spain%2C%20Germany%20or%20Ireland.%20They%20can%20follow%20courses%20and%20learn%20better%20about%20the%20languages%2C%20the%20cultures%20and%20traditions%20of%20these%20countries.%20\",\"In%20particular%2C%20San%20Vito%20al%20Tagliamento%20is%20twinned%20with%20a%20town%20called%20Stadthlon%20which%20is%20in%20the%20north%20of%20Germany.%20This%20year%20they%20are%20celebrating%20their%2040th%20anniversary%21%20Our%20school%20has%20a%20special%20exchange%20programme%20with%20the%20Gymnasium%20school%20based%20in%20Stadthlon.%20Every%20year%20classes%20from%20our%20school%20go%20there%20for%20a%20week%20and%20then%20German%20students%20come%20to%20San%20Vito.%20There%20is%20a%20long%20lasting%20friendship%20between%20the%20two%20towns%3A%20in%20fact%20at%20the%20moment%20a%20group%20of%20German%20representatives%20are%20here%20for%20the%20celebrations.%20\",\"During%20the%20summer%20holidays%2C%20any%20student%20in%20our%20school%20can%20consider%20the%20possibility%20to%20take%20part%20in%20a%20study-holiday%20in%20England%20or%20Ireland.%20This%20project%20is%20organized%20every%20year%20for%20the%20first%20two%20weeks%20of%20September%20before%20school%20starts.%20During%20this%20time%20students%20are%20hosted%20by%20a%20family.%20In%20the%20morning%20you%20go%20to%20school%20which%20usually%20starts%20at%208.30%20and%20you%20attend%20mixed%20classes%20where%20you%20can%20meet%20students%20from%20other%20countries%20and%20of%20course%2C%20everybody%20will%20be%20speaking%20English%21%20\",\"When%20school%20ends%2C%20in%20the%20afternoon%20there%20are%20many%20other%20activities%3A%20for%20example%2C%20excursions%20to%20visit%20different%20cities%20to%20see%20cathedrals%2C%20museums%20and%20go%20shopping%20in%20your%20free%20time%21%20In%20the%20evenings%20after%20dinner%20with%20your%20family%2C%20the%20school%20organizes%20other%20things%20like%20sports%2C%20bowling%2C%20cinema%2C%20disco%20or%20even%20a%20night%20out%20for%20some%20traditional%20fish%20%E2%80%98n%20chips%21%20\",\"All%20in%20all%2C%20our%20school%20is%20really%20dynamic%20and%20lively%20so%20we%20are%20happy%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20community%21%20\"]', 'https://i.ibb.co/5j7f7hG/IMG5.png', 'https://i.ibb.co/5j7f7hG/IMG5.png', '{\"intervista\":\"\",\"in lingua\":\"1\",\"politica studentesca\":\"\",\"fatti dal mondo\":\"\",\"salute e benessere\":\"\",\"editoriale\":\"\"}'),
(6, 'Correre al traguardo', 'Mattia Paissan, Jason De Lorenzi, Gabriele Marson – Redazione 22-23', 'Dentro alla professione, alle passioni e alla vita privata di due insegnanti della nostra scuola: intervista ai Prof. Roberto Piccoli e Rocco Garripoli ', '2024-05-30', '[\"%3Cb%3EPROF.%20ROBERTO%20PICCOLI%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"%3Cb%3EProf%2C%20che%20sport%20faceva%20da%20piccolo%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Ho%20fatto%20calcio%20dai%206%2F7%20anni%20fino%20ai%2030.%20Attualmente%20pratico%20il%20tennis.%20Mi%20piacciono%20soprattutto%20gli%20sport%20di%20squadra%20e%20la%20possibilit%C3%A0%20di%20improvvisare.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EPerch%C3%A9%20ha%20deciso%20di%20diventare%20un%20prof%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Sono%20andato%20all%E2%80%99universit%C3%A0%20per%20un%20anno%20a%20fare%20giurisprudenza%2C%20ho%20fatto%20un%20esame%20e%20basta%20e%20ho%20chiuso%20con%20la%20media%2029%20%28risate%2C%20ndr%29.%20Mio%20padre%20era%20allenatore%20di%20calcio%20e%20mia%20madre%20era%20una%20pallavolista%20di%20serie%20A%2C%20quindi%20ho%20ereditato%20la%20passione%20per%20le%20scienze%20motorie.%20\",\"%3Cb%3ELe%20piace%20di%20pi%C3%B9%20lavorare%20a%20scuola%20o%20in%20societ%C3%A0%20sportive%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Se%20mi%20aveste%20fatto%20la%20domanda%204%20anni%20fa%20vi%20avrei%20detto%20le%20societ%C3%A0%20sportive%20perch%C3%A9%20c%E2%80%99%C3%A8%20pi%C3%B9%20competitivit%C3%A0%20e%20la%20possibilit%C3%A0%20di%20portare%20la%20squadra%20a%20un%20risultato.%20Adesso%20invece%20mi%20piace%20la%20scuola%20perch%C3%A9%20%C3%A8%20divertente%20stare%20con%20gli%20alunni.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EHa%20trovato%20difficolt%C3%A0%20in%20questi%20ultimi%20anni%20da%20insegnante%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"No%2C%20ho%20girato%20molte%20scuole%20tra%20istituti%20comprensivi%20e%20altro%E2%80%A6%20\",\"%3Cb%3EQual%20%C3%A8%20lo%20sport%20preferito%20che%20insegna%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Il%20mio%20sport%20preferito%20%C3%A8%20la%20pallamano%20perch%C3%A9%20si%20pu%C3%B2%20fare%20gruppo%20sportivo%20per%20andare%20contro%20le%20altre%20s