(7, 'Zoom sul problema dei Disturbi Alimentari', 'Hajar El Kourrati – Redazione 22-23', 'Che cos’è un Disturbo Alimentare? Quante sono le tipologie? Quali i pericoli per la salute? Questo articolo cerca di far luce su un problema che affligge soprattutto i giovani. ', '2024-05-30', '[\"Il%2027%20marzo%20%282023%2C%20ndr%29%20noi%20studenti%20siamo%20andati%20all%E2%80%99assemblea%20in%20auditorium%20H.%20Zotti%20che%20trattava%20i%20disturbi%20alimentari.%20Grazie%20all%E2%80%99intervento%20della%20psicologa%20abbiamo%20potuto%20capire%20meglio%20cosa%20sono%20i%20disturbi%20alimentari%3A%20sono%20delle%20patologie%20caratterizzate%20da%20disfunzioni%20del%20comportamento%20alimentare%20nelle%20quali%20emerge%20un%E2%80%99eccessiva%20preoccupazione%20per%20il%20peso%2C%20con%20una%20visione%20alterata%20del%20proprio%20corpo.%20Questi%20disturbi%20danneggiano%20sia%20la%20salute%20fisica%20sia%20il%20funzionamento%20psicologico.%20\",\"Nella%20maggior%20parte%20dei%20casi%20questa%20condizione%20nasce%20da%20un%20senso%20di%20colpa.%20Le%20cause%20principali%20possono%20essere%20un%E2%80%99eccessiva%20preoccupazione%2C%20bassa%20autostima%2C%20la%20tendenza%20al%20perfezionismo%2C%20situazioni%20particolarmente%20stressanti%20al%20lavoro%20o%20a%20scuola%20e%20la%20depressione.\",\"%3Cb%3ETIPI%20DI%20DISTURBI%20ALIMENTARI%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Esistono%20diverse%20tipi%20di%20patologie%20dei%20disturbi%20alimentari.%20Questi%20sono%3A%20la%20bulimia%20nervosa%2C%20l%E2%80%99anoressia%20nervosa%2C%20l%E2%80%99ortoressia%20nervosa%2C%20la%20drunkoressia%2C%20la%20vigoressia%2C%20la%20pregoressia.\",\"Bulimia%20nervosa%5CnLe%20persone%20che%20sono%20colpite%20da%20questa%20patologia%20hanno%20l%E2%80%99obiettivo%20di%20controllare%20il%20loro%20peso%2C%20diminuendo%20la%20quantit%C3%A0%20di%20cibo%20nel%20loro%20corpo%20e%20successivamente%20si%20abbuffano.%20Dopo%20l%E2%80%99abbuffata%2C%20arrivano%20i%20sensi%20di%20colpa.%20Quindi%20per%20liberarsi%20dal%20cibo%20ingerito%2C%20si%20procurano%20il%20vomito%20e%2Fo%20prendono%20lassativi.%20Esistono%20due%20tipi%20di%20abbuffate%3A%20quelle%20oggettive%20e%20quelle%20soggettive.%20L%E2%80%99abbuffata%20oggettiva%20%C3%A8%20quella%20dove%20si%20introduce%20un%20grande%20quantit%C3%A0%20di%20cibo.%20L%E2%80%99abbuffata%20soggettiva%20%C3%A8%20quando%20la%20persona%20crede%20di%20aver%20perso%20il%20controllo%20della%20situazione%2C%20non%20rispettando%20quindi%20le%20regole%20alimentari%20che%20si%20era%20prefissata.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EAnoressia%20nervosa%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Le%20persone%20che%20hanno%20l%E2%80%99anoressia%20nervosa%2C%20cercano%20di%20dimagrire%2C%20quindi%20di%20perdere%20molto%20peso%2C%20attraverso%20la%20restrizione%20diabetica.%20Le%20cause%20primarie%20sono%20la%20bassa%20autostima%20e%20la%20continua%20ricerca%20di%20perfezione.%20Un%20grosso%20disturbo%20che%20ne%20consegue%20%C3%A8%20la%20dismorfofobia.%20Questo%20%C3%A8%20la%20percezione%20alterata%20del%20nostro%20corpo.%20L%E2%80%99anoressia%20inizia%20spesso%20con%20una%20dieta%20della%20quale%20poi%20si%20perde%20il%20controllo.%20Queste%20persone%20per%20perdere%20peso%20obbligano%20la%20loro%20mente%20a%20non%20sentire%20la%20fame.%20Saltano%20pasti%2C%20mangiano%20pochissimo%20e%20in%20alcuni%20periodi%20non%20mangiano%20niente%2C%20contano%20ossessivamente%20le%20calorie%20del%20cibo%3B%20praticano%20attivit%C3%A0%20fisica%20eccessiva.%20Successivamente%20il%20cervello%20mette%20in%20pratica%20meccanismi%20di%20difesa%20che%20comportano%20dei%20cambiamenti%20fisici%20come%20l%E2%80%99eliminazione%20del%20ciclo%20mestruale%20o%20la%20crescita%20di%20peli%20esagerata%20atta%20a%20proteggere%20il%20corpo%20dal%20freddo%2C%20le%20unghie%20e%20i%20capelli%20diventano%20pi%C3%B9%20fragili.%20Il%20cuore%20rallenta%20il%20suo%20battito%20cardiaco%20fino%20a%20raggiungere%20livelli%20pericolosi%20di%20brachicardia.%20I%20fattori%20psicologici%20dell%E2%80%99anoressia%20sono%3A%20tendenza%20alla%20depressione%20e%20all%E2%8