(11, 'La mia vita dopo Le Filandiere ', 'Francesca Nonis, Omar Madi, Alice Tondat – Redazione 22-23', 'L’ex liceale e futuro ingegnere, Brayan Zamarian, rivive in questa intervista il suo passato alle Filandiere e ci racconta della sua attuale esperienza universitaria. ', '2024-05-30', '[\"%3Cb%3EPerch%C3%A9%20hai%20scelto%20le%20Filandiere%20e%20che%20indirizzo%20hai%20frequentato%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Ho%20scelto%20le%20Filandiere%20perch%C3%A9%20non%20avevo%20ancora%20chiare%20le%20idee%20sul%20mio%20futuro%20quindi%20volevo%20una%20scuola%20che%20mi%20potesse%20preparare%20il%20pi%C3%B9%20possibile%20a%20360%C2%B0.%20Come%20indirizzo%20ho%20scelto%20quello%20delle%20Scienze%20Applicate%20perch%C3%A9%20mi%20sentivo%20poco%20attratto%20dalle%20materie%20umanistiche.%20\",\"%3Cb%3ECome%20ti%20sei%20trovato%20in%20questi%20cinque%20anni%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E\",\"Nei%20miei%20cinque%20anni%20di%20superiori%20mi%20sono%20trovato%20quasi%20sempre%20bene%20sia%20con%20i%20professori%20che%20con%20i%20miei%20compagni.%20Libri%20e%20spiegazioni%20hanno%20sempre%20permesso%20una%20preparazione%20adeguata%20per%20affrontare%20interrogazioni%20e%20verifiche.%20\",\"Come%20hai%20affrontato%20la%20maturit%C3%A0%20e%20con%20quanto%20sei%20uscito%3F%20\",\"La%20maturit%C3%A0%20%C3%A8%20stata%20sicuramente%20la%20prova%20pi%C3%B9%20difficile%20di%20questi%20cinque%20anni.%20Ero%20riuscito%20ad%20ottenere%20una%20buona%20media%20per%20tutto%20il%20triennio%20garantendomi%20un%20buon%20ammontare%20di%20crediti.%20Per%20questo%20ero%20abbastanza%20sicuro%20che%20sarei%20riuscito%20a%20passare%20l%E2%80%99esame%20ma%20sapevo%20anche%20che%20avrei%20dovuto%20soddisfare%20le%20aspettative%20uscendo%20con%20un%20voto%20alto%20e%20questo%20mi%20metteva%20molta%20ansia.%20Alla%20fine%2C%20sono%20riuscito%20a%20diplomarmi%20con%2096%2F100%20e%20a%20chiudere%20in%20maniera%20soddisfacente%20il%20mio%20percorso%20al%20liceo.%20\",\"%3Cb%3EPensi%20che%20questa%20scuola%20ti%20prepari%20al%20meglio%20